    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 78-81.</p><p>Memorized Spellbook</p><p>When you reach 24th level, your Spellbook has become obsolete. You have memorized all the contents from your Spellbook and no longer require it to cast Ritual spells. You have all spells from your Spellbook prepared at any time. Whenever you add a spell to your Spellbook, you immediately memorize it and always have it prepared.</p><p>You no longer require an arcane focus to cast spells, using your mind as your arcane focus.</p></div>",
